    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Aggregate consisting of fine sand, crushed stone, or crushed slag screenings added to mortar, stucco, or concrete for strength and stability as well as to minimize shrinkage.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
